subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Tony Stewart led 66 of 160 laps, grabbing the lead for good from Kevin Harvick with 10 laps left for his second consecutive Nextel Cup victory.
